profile: We are a family owned specialty Appliance store. We are in our 33rd year of business serving Stony Plain and the surrounding area. We carry specialty brands including Bosch, LG, GE, Wolf, Sub-Zero, Thermador and Fisher Paykel. Our expert consultants will help you with your appliance purchases. We offer in house delivery and set up. We service your appliances as well in case there is a service issue. Come in and see our live kitchens with the latest in design and function!
